Description
===========
This adds a Command Line Interface to my checkers gem, viewable at https://github.com/mikeweber/checkers

Install
=======
This gem uses Bundler for dependency management. With the repo downloaded, run `bundle` to install the Checkers dependency.

How to play
===========
From the root directory, run `bundle exec irb -r ./lib/cli_checkers`
Then from IRB, run `CliGame.play`
